This extension of linum can control the width of line
numbers displayed based on the line number of the point at the end of the current window or buffer.

See also: LineNumbers, LinumMode

==Installation==

Copy linum+.el from [https://github.com/emacsmirror/linum-plus emacsmirror/linum-plus] to your load-path and add to your .emacs:

    (require 'linum+)

then use <kbd>M-x linum-mode</kbd> to display line numbers



